Package: ggmultivar
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate Analysis Plots Using ggplot2
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Jannik Vindeloev
Maintainer: Jannik Vindeloev <jannik.vindeloev@example.com>
Description: Create scores and loading plots for multivariate analysis using ggplot2 syntax. The package provides S3 methods for mixOmics objects and custom geoms for confidence intervals and encircling groups. Designed for layer-by-layer plot customization.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    purrr,
    tibble,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    covr,
    mixOmics
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/JannikVindeloev/ggmultivar
